text: Just to put things in perspective, they're saying the structures go up to 2km deep; that's over a MILE deep. These ancient pyramids were the tallest manmade structures on earth until the Lincoln Cathedral was made in 1311, almost 4 MILLENNIA later, and the tallest pyramid ONLY goes ~0.15km high. These structures underneath the pyramid are over THIRTEEN times deeper than the height of the pyramid that held the height record for over 3800 years. Even the current tallest building in the world isn't even 1km high, and even some of the current deepest structures barely surpass 2km and only did so in the last 25 years. If this turns out to be true, this would be one of the most astonishing ancient discoveries of all time, and it will completely rewrite history.

Flood waters and moving silt are how we get rock layers in a matter of a few months and also fossils, just like at Mount Saint Helens in Washington that only blew in 1980.
